akas: Young Hollywood Presents Evolution Of... USA (complete title)
akas from release info: Young Hollywood Presents Evolution Of... USA (complete title)

1.title: Modern Family
1.plot: A star-studded journey inside the stories one of television's best comedies, straight from the celebs themselves: find out how far Sofia Vergara will go to maintain her appearance, and why Ty Burrel almost quit acting before Modern Family.

2.title: Wonder Girls
2.plot: Explore the wonderful, musical world of Wonder Girls; from their start on South Korean reality TV to their explosion on the international pop charts and the life changing event that threatened to break them up for good.

3.title: Sean Kingston
3.plot: Follow the roller-coaster story of pop star Sean Kingston, from his troubled childhood in Jamaica through his success as an international pop star, and to the accident that nearly took his life.

4.title: Big Time Rush
4.plot: A captivating look at the evolution of "Big Time Rush": the Nickelodeon quartet that survived a brutal two-year audition to find each other, and went on to conquer television and music around the world.

5.title: Teen Wolf
5.plot: Tyler Posey, Dylan O'Brien, and the rest of Teen Wolf cast share their ups and downs, most embarrassing moments, and stories straight from the set of one of MTV's hottest shows.

6.title: Far East Movement
6.plot: Far East Movement shares their stories of success and struggle, from playing local L.A. clubs to touring with Lady Gaga and recording with Justin Bieber; featuring exclusive footage from the set of "Like a G6" and "The Illest".

7.title: Paris Hilton
7.plot: Explore the star-studded story of Paris Hilton: from her beginnings as a "celebutante" and red carpet darling to her adventures in reality television and the rise of her worldwide media and business empire.

8.title: Ne-Yo
8.plot: An in-depth look at R&B chart-topper Ne-Yo: his early struggles, how he earned his name, his collaborations with music legends, and the stories behind some of his biggest songs.

9.title: LMFAO
9.plot: Strap in for a roller coaster story of Redfoo and Skyblu, the dynamic duo behind LMFAO; featuring multiple crazy interviews with the boys in their home, back stage, and on tour.

10.title: Emblem3
10.plot: Do not call them a boy band! This episode of "Evolution Of..." follows Emblem3 through their early years as music hopefuls in Washington State, and down into the L.A. music scene. With their own brand of silly seriousness, the boys describe the hardships of X-Factor boot camp, their vision for their music, and the challenges of life in one of the toughest talent competitions in the world. Featuring interviews with Simon Cowell and Demi Lovato, as well as Emblem3's take on touring with Selena Gomez.

11.title: iCarly
11.plot: An inside look at Miranda Cosgrove, Jennette McCurdy, and Nathan Kress from "iCarly," including the secret to the show's outrageous success, and an attempt to put the Sam/Carly/Freddie love triangle to rest once and for all.

12.title: Twilight
12.plot: The cast of Twilight shares stories and memories from on and off the set of the Twilight series; features interviews with Kristin Stewart, Taylor Lautner, and many more.

13.title: The Kardashians
13.plot: An exclusive peek into the exotic lives of Kim Kardashian and sisters Khloe and Kourtney, following their early adventures from Hollywood's best-kept fashion secret to reality television mega stars.

1.title: Pretty Little Liars
1.plot: The inside story on "Pretty Little Liars," from its beginning as a book series to its success on television; featuring interviews with the cast and exclusive breakdowns of the girls' fashion with costume designer Mandi Line.

2.title: Victoria Justice
2.plot: An in-depth series of interviews with Victoria Justice, spanning her life in television, video games, music, and film.

3.title: Lady Gaga
3.plot: An inside look at Lady Gaga's evolution from a New York rock musician to the world's biggest pop diva; featuring interviews and footage from the set of her first hit "Pokerface," and the story of how she got her name.

4.title: Snoop Dogg
4.plot: An in-depth look at Snoop Dogg: his early collaborations with Dr. Dre, the albums that transformed him into a hip-hop legend, and his "reincarnation" as Snoop Lion.

5.title: Jordin Sparks
5.plot: An in-depth look at pop icon Jordin Sparks: from becoming the youngest American Idol winner in history to her passionate relationship with Jason DeRulo, and the grueling travel schedule that nearly cost her her career.

6.title: Selena Gomez
6.plot: An in-depth look at the sparkling career of Selena Gomez: from her childhood start on Barney the Dinosaur and her adolescent romance with Justin Bieber to her worldwide success in music and television.

7.title: The Hunger Games
7.plot: Go behind the scenes in the evolution of The Hunger Games, through interviews with the cast; includes the true stories of how Josh Hutcherson talked his way into a film career, and the nature of his "bromance" with Sam Claflin.

8.title: Demi Lovato
8.plot: Follow acting sensation-turned-pop diva Demi Lovato, from her early years on Barney the Dinosaur to her debut as a mature, seasoned mentor on the X-Factor; featuring interviews with Demi Lovato, Simon Cowell, and L.A. Reid.

9.title: Vampire Diaries
9.plot: Nina Dobrev, Ian Somerhalder, and the cast of the Vampire Diaries spill the stories behind one of the most popular CW shows in history; find out what makes the perfect vampire face, and how Somerhalder almost missed his chance to audition.

10.title: Glee
10.plot: An intimate look at the evolution of the cast of Glee; from their beginnings as Young Hollywood hopefuls, to their triumphs as musical stars; featuring an exclusive in-depth interview with Cory Monteith.

11.title: Cody Simpson
11.plot: An in-depth look at Cody Simpson's rise to stardom: his early success on YouTube, his collaborations with Justin Bieber, and his current status as an international pop star.

12.title: Mindless Behavior
12.plot: A fast-paced ride through the lives of Mindless Behavior: Prodigy, Princeton, Ray Ray, and Roc Royal share the stories behind their names, their group, their performance for the President, and much more.

13.title: Ryan Sheckler
13.plot: An up-close look at the career of Ryan Sheckler: from the secrets of life as a professional skateboarder to the accident that cost him a gold medal; featuring interviews throughout Ryan's career.

imdb.plot outline: Features a range of A-listers that Young Hollywood has been following since the very beginning of their careers. From past to present, see how your favorite celebrities have developed from wide-eyed hopefuls into bona fide superstars. Featuring early photo shoots, exclusive interviews and set visits, Young Hollywood shows how these stars have evolved throughout the years.
